 Renault  Dacia  Nissan  Toyota Bath  Toyota Trowbridge  Skoda  Hyundai Chippenham  Hyundai Frome  Vauxhall   Reviews Links     Gender Pay Gap Reporting        The Platinum Motor Group (Renrod Ltd) is committed to ensuring that no gender related pay gaps exist within the company. It is considered that where pay differences exist, they are based on experience and overall levels of responsibility in any given role.  At Platinum, like the wider automotive industry, we employ more male team members than other genders, which the industry has historically and traditionally attracted. We do believe however, that gender is absolutely no barrier to employment within the Platinum Group and we will continue to warmly welcome team members of all genders with the relevant skill sets, experience, enthusiasm and potential to contribute to the success of the company.  The Gender Pay Gap Reporting has been collated by the company and submitted to the Government UK website.  View our report here .        Want us to call you back?  Enter your details & we'll get back to you within 1 working day                 Please Select...  Callback Request Dacia Trowbridge Parts  Callback Request Dacia Trowbridge Sales  Callback Request Dacia Trowbridge Service  Callback Request Hyundai Chippenham Parts  Callback Request Hyundai Chippenham Sales  Callback Request Hyundai Chippenham Service  Callback Request Hyundai Frome Parts  Callback Request Hyundai Frome Sales  Callback Request Hyundai Frome Service  Callback Request Nissan Bath Parts  Callback Request Nissan Bath Sales  Callback Request Nissan Bath Service  Callback Request Nissan Trowbridge Parts  Callback Request Nissan Trowbridge Sales  Callback Request Nissan Trowbridge Service  Callback Request Renault Bath Parts  Callback Request Renault Bath Service  Callback Request Renault Chippenham Parts  Callback Request Renault Chippenham Service  Callback Request Renault Trowbridge Parts  Callback Request Renault Trowbridge Sales  Callback Requ